      "title": "LAUGFS lowers 12.5kg cylinder price by Rs.1,050",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The price of a 12.5kg domestic LAUGFS gas cylinder was reduced by Rs. 1,050 from midnight today, LAUGFS Holdings founder and Chairman W.K.H. Wegapitiya said.",
        "Accordingly, the new retail price of the 12.5 kg gas cylinder will be Rs. 5,800. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
